The '''Dubrillion Aquarium''' was an [[Aquarium/Legends|aquarium]] in [[Dubrillion/Legends|Dubrillion's]] [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]]. It contained [[Transparisteel/Legends|transparisteel]] tanks filled with [[Fish/Legends|fish]] from Dubrillion and other [[Planet/Legends|worlds]], dominated by a central cylindrical tank filled with big [[emerald shark]]s and rainbow fish. [[Shedao Shai]] made it his headquarters during the early stages of the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], after the [[evacuation of Dubrillion]].

